6:
That was a pretty solid beating you
handed them, Mia! And here you
were grumbling about fighting.
8:
With skills like that you could easily
survive on your own, even in the
shadier parts of town!
12: I'm not sure I want to...
15:
Honey buns, isn't it a tad early to let
your guard down?
27:
Confound it! So close, yet so far!
Pray make the next spin your
winning one, fair pirate! I fear my
stomach may not survive another
round...
31:
Oh my sweet, innocent prince! Your
naivete is truly GORGEOUS!
35:
Hold on... Are you perchance...
Employing underhanded tricks of
some sort?!
43:
And they too are absolutely
BEAUTIFUL!
48:
I question your ability to accurately
appraise true beauty!
51:
Oh, darling. Beauty is in the eye of
the beholder, don't you know?
53:
Still, I'm worried about your stamina,
Illumine! If you keep this up, your
precious little body will give out.
57:
Ngh... You might be right about that.
I'm starting to feel the exhaustion hit
me already...
60:
The moment we hear word from Alk
and the rest, we split—
64:
Hold on a second. My tiger senses
are tingling...
70:
Alk! What are you doing over here?
This isn't where we agreed to
regroup—
74:
Sorry, Marina! There's no time to
explain, it's an emergency!
80:
Aaalk! This giant, gross, creepy thing
is chasing after us!
84:
It's just like the ones that attacked
us before!
88:
Only much bigger.
Still, nice of it to attack us head on
like this.
92:
I was getting bored of staring at that
slot machine anyway!
97:
Good timin' too. Right after I got
worked up about losing all that
money. Now I can take my anger
out on this thing!
102: Well, when you put it that way!
105:
Let's show this thing what we're
made of!
